beer.beer_description: Bright golden yellow color and aromas of rich tropical fruit, passion fruit with a hint of citrus.  Pale, pilsner, and midnight wheat give it a solid malt character while Chinook, Citra, and Amarillo hops impart flavors of ripe tropical fruit, peach and apricot leading to a clean hoppy finish.
